/**
 * H3D (Holistic Health & Home Defense) single-file website
 *
 * How to customize quickly (no code hunting):
 * 1) Edit BRAND + CONTACT constants.
 * 2) Edit the CONTENT arrays: FITNESS_OFFERS, FIREARMS_OFFERS, GALLERY.
 * 3) Replace placeholder images with your own URLs.
 *
 * Notes:
 * - This site is intentionally "launch-ready" as a clean landing site.
 * - Firearms content is framed around safety, responsibility, and fundamentals.
 */

